codex
The main risk surface is now clear: reward accounting relies on `balance - sFLOOR.circulatingSupply()` while the contract separately tracks off-ledger liabilities in warmup and wrapper flows. I’m validating whether those liabilities are ever incorporated locally; if not, that’s an insolvency class issue rather than a cosmetic accounting bug.
